description: This source file sets up the entry point for a React application by importing necessary modules, including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component, then renders the App component within the DOM element with id 'root' within React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root to enable rendering of React components into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the created React root.
